name: Witchy Woods (Starlette Games)
description:
Description

Witchy Woods is a Difficult Platformer, It's Got Only 6 Levels but You Have Lots of Movement Options and a Boss at The End, It's Only Available for Windows Though.

Controls

Z  - Jump

X  -  Attack

C - Dash

S  - Interact 

Story

Idk... You Got Trapped by The Candy Man or somethin'.

Features

Dashin
